# This file is used to specify which parts can be saved. Without it, the player will not be able to save creations which use your mod's parts.
# Note that this file does not contain a list of parts at all. That's because this file inherits from the one in ce_EditorKeys~, meaning that
# only one list has to be maintained, rather than several.

# This file's name should always be unique to your mod. If two mods add files which use the same filename, the file from one of them will be ignored.
# Such conflicts can often be avoided by including your mod's name or a unique abbreviation of it in your files' names. This applies to most files in a mod.


key parent ce_EditorKeys~!vehice.prop